{"tid":1401027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"校園暴力，不可容忍","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:14.000Z","uid":27085,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6facdb083327533644742708c7603c3070b24511","tid":1401027,"uid":27085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:09:41.000Z","msg":"其實面對校園暴力，被害人根本唔可以硬碰硬<br />\n你會比人bully係因為你地physical condition好過你<br />\n你如果同佢硬頸，你只會慢慢咁打到你殘<br />\n最後消磨你嘅意志<br />\n然後只會唔甘心咁接受被bully嘅現實<br />\n甚至甘心接心被bully嘅現實<br />\n<br />\n相反，如果你可以捉住施暴者嘅心態<br />\n識得走精面，適當地走位<br />\n例如激嬲佢但又係又可以令佢到冇機會打你<br />\n姐係激將法<br />\n到最後佢只會鬱鬱而終<br />\n冇地方發洩<br />\n而你可以脫離到校園暴力<br />\n成為勝方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7028aff0e1b51057584adb4814927798406e5e30","tid":1401027,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:10:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35f1bd1d8373162ec3d5cbb02d0225467616c6fa","tid":1401027,"uid":27085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"自己曾經係校園暴力受害者<br />\n希望同大家分享心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1eb635f1029afece18b632e3de41d47985f168","tid":1401027,"uid":27085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"好似開錯台，不過都希望大家明白依個簡淺嘅大道理"},{"pid":"41bd0726ec5869ccc2c9436b2e68ff419938377f","tid":1401027,"uid":27085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d964286b08d8079b914dc6a77a96421ea12c021b","tid":1401027,"uid":27085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"238547ac66734fc11e1ffc7b487bac84f